# VEHICLE::SET_CARGOBOB_PICKUP_ROPE_DAMPING_MULTIPLIER

## Summary
Specifiy a multiplier that modifies the strength of the damping force applied to the entity attached to the pick-up rope

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **FLOAT** dampingMult
